---
import Logo from './Logo.astro';
---

<section class="bg-white py-16 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
    <!-- Left: Quote & Text -->
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <p class="section-label">Comunidad de Élite</p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Comunidad Privada &
        <br />
        <span class="text-brand-gold">Networking</span>
      </h2>

      <!-- Quote -->
      <blockquote class="relative">
        <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-gold to-brand-gold/20 rounded-full"></div>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed italic pl-8">
          "No solo entregamos títulos, construimos carreras de alto nivel. Cada alumno tiene acceso de por vida a la red privada de alumnos y contactos para asegurar su éxito en el mercado real."
        </p>
      </blockquote>

     

      <div class="pt-6 pl-8">
        <button class="trigger-admission-modal cta-button px-10 py-4 text-base shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition-all">
          SOLICITAR ADMISIÓN
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Feature Card -->
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Decorative blur -->
      <div class="absolute -top-12 -left-12 w-48 h-48 bg-brand-gold/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 w-36 h-36 bg-brand-navy/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

      <div class="relative bg-brand-navy rounded-brand-xl p-10 md:p-12 text-white space-y-8 shadow-2xl">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
          <div class="h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
            <Logo class="h-full w-auto" />
          </div>
          <div class="h-px w-8 bg-white/20 rotate-90 -ml-4 hidden md:block"></div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-extrabold leading-tight">Acceso Exclusivo</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-brand-gold uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Solo para alumnos Osbord</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Divider -->
        <div class="w-full h-px bg-white/10"></div>

        <!-- Features -->
        <ul class="space-y-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-gold/20 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-white">Networking Global</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Conexión con alumnos y profesionales en todo el mundo.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-gold/20 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-white">Sesiones Preguntas y Respuestas</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Sesiones de preguntas y respuestas con especialistas de la industria.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-gold/20 flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-white">Bolsa de Empleo Exclusiva</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Oportunidades de alto perfil seleccionadas para nuestra comunidad global de graduados.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
